schemaFilePath

protected java.lang.String schemaFilePath
Table schema is represented by SanchayTableModel itself. The common attributes for a schema are: ColumnName, DataType, DefaultValue, PropType, PropFile. Each row of schema table will represent one column (attribute) of this table. The schema table (and schemaFile and schemaCharset) of the schema table will be null.
